  ('optometrist-moex-00696', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Snellenchart之視力為6/30的患者，其萬國視力、最小分辨角及logMAR值分別為多少？（log1=0,log2=0.3, log5=0.7,log10=1）', '["0.2、5.0、0.3", "0.2、5.0、0.7", "0.2、0.2、0.7", "5.0、0.2、0.7"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00697', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關Purkinje影像的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["PurkinjeI、II、III影像為正立虛像，PurkinjeIV影像為倒立實像", "當眼球在調節時，水晶體前表面的曲率半徑減小，PurkinjeIII影像的尺寸也會縮小", "透過觀察PurkinjeII影像，可以量測斜視角度", "角膜地形圖是藉由PurkinjeI影像來測定角膜的形狀"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00698', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個簡化眼的總屈光力為+60.00D，剛好被眼前12mm處的-12.50D鏡片完全矯正，則此眼球的眼軸長為何？', '["27.52mm", "27.13mm", "26.52mm", "25.95mm"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
